title: Grateful Dead Live at Meadowlands Arena on 1988-04-01
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step-> Jack Straw-> To Lay Me Down, Ballad Of A Thin Man, When Push Comes To Shove, Minglewood Blues, Cumberland Blues, Deal

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace

April fool Bobby Begining of first set: "We'll see ya later!"
